Category:Personnel of Ysanne Isard's Thyferran regime

nodes.text: 73 was the designation of an Imperial stormtrooper stationed on the spaceport of Thyferra. A short firefight ensued when another stormtrooper tried to arrest Corran Horn, who was under disguise; during the course of the battle 73 fell from an elevated walkway along with Horn.
